name: Infinite Waves
description:
The idea for a prompt can (and should) come from any direction.  In this case it was the name of a blogger who had just interviewed me, who goes by the name 'Infinite Waves'.

So I used his name as the prompt.  CLIP never fails to amaze me in how it interprets a phrase.  Here it understands and expresses infinity by depicting recursion and repetition in the crests of ocean waves.  

Made with Text to Image synthesis (CLIP & VQGan)
